# Peer Voting App

## Design

Have you ever been at a movie theatre with your friends and can't decide which movie to watch? The Peer Voting App can fix that! When you login to this app, you can select from a variety of questions, like what movie to watch, what restaurant to eat at, what color is the best, and much more! The best part is that you can see how many people voted for each choice in real time! Get the Peer Voting App now to start settle all your disputes today.

<img width="590" alt="Screen Shot 2023-02-05 at 3 29 06 PM" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/91141889/216849613-eba2cdd4-12e5-4241-a58b-d0d4c524c62d.png">

## Key Features

 - Connects online with your friends to see the groups' answers
 - Account login to save your profile
 - Select from a drop-down of questions/polls
 - See total votes for each choice updated in real time
 - Votes to questions saved in a database
 - See account name in top of screen
